WEBVTT

00:03.894 --> 00:05.396
‐ That workshop,
if I hadn't taken it,

00:05.396 --> 00:06.482
I'd be so fucked.
‐ Well, you have me now.

00:06.482 --> 00:08.026
24‐hour service.

00:08.026 --> 00:09.572
I think something bad
happened to me

00:09.572 --> 00:11.367
a long time ago
when I was a child.

00:11.367 --> 00:13.037
Well, I have to
get out of here.

00:13.037 --> 00:14.707
‐ You mean leave right now?
‐ Yeah, I'm gonna

00:14.707 --> 00:16.418
talk to Harold, we'll get
our things together.

00:16.418 --> 00:18.047
- Where are we going?
- Back to New York.

00:18.047 --> 00:20.301
‐ To the compound?
‐ I'm taking it back.

00:20.301 --> 00:21.721
‐ Eddie's hired an SL.

00:21.721 --> 00:24.017
Secular Liaison.
She's a publicist.

00:24.017 --> 00:27.440
‐ I have decided to
take down the guard booth.

00:27.440 --> 00:30.280
If anyone's here,
it's time to come out.

00:31.741 --> 00:33.912
He is just a kid.
We can help him.

00:33.912 --> 00:36.333
‐ My husband's away and I need
to keep my family safe.

00:36.333 --> 00:38.421
There was a bomb threat
in Spring Valley.

00:38.421 --> 00:41.093
‐ Look, the kid is not
building a bomb.

00:45.811 --> 00:48.734
‐ My life's work is studying
new American faiths.

00:48.734 --> 00:51.363
‐ I recently
came across something

00:51.363 --> 00:52.825
that Steve used to use.

00:52.825 --> 00:54.829
The Hypoxian Cleanse.

00:54.829 --> 00:56.666
Listen, if the
Hypoxian Cleanse is in there,

00:56.666 --> 00:58.502
who knows what else there is?

